{"type": "article", "id": 18307, "title": "立体书", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-01T07:20:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134805YeaJgs2d30uynmj1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是日本建筑师大野友资设计的两本立体书，分别以富士山和白雪公主为主题。他将每一页做了不同的镂空设计，打开后形成立体的图像，让富士山或森林形成立体的图景，穿插平面的人物和动植物做点缀，很有层次感。既可以平摊在桌面，也可以将封面和封底叠在一起，360 度旋转查看，成为小型的桌面装饰。像是结合儿童的立体书和建筑模型，有一种纯真的折纸感和巧妙的设计感。<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/360%C2%B0BOOK-%E7%99%BD%E9%9B%AA%E5%A7%AB-SNOW-WHITE-%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8E/dp/4861525179/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1448492738&amp;sr=1-1\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021348022CvPU3Qfhkwb7GJs.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134802K7FXDBMon0ZC4OAJ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021348039byWMHIfhPL1zck5.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134803m9RgiUYNKsbEOp0S.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021348046vpAxFQ902JZfC71.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134804FZpWzlequVH3iAQX.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"429\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}